<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
	<div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
		<h2>About</h2>
		<hr>
		<p>I am a developer living in Nashville, TN.</p>
		<p>Day job? No, not really. Other than running my <a href="http://www.cleverladder.co">web design &amp; development business</a>, I work in Live Entertainment.</p>
